Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:18.26,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnFZLanTingHei-L-GBK\fax-0.15\fad(150,0)\frz328.1\c&HE0E5E4&\pos(384,406)}傍晚 爸爸的車會去接你
